regulator: qcom_rpm: Fix circular deferral regression

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v4.14.296 by commit 8f96d64429b30e369584b36f7612661c8961f199, it was introduced in version v4.1 by commit 087a1b5cdd555970feb8a340dc008b6914f05128. For more details please see the references link.
